          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A\to  B]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g\colon  B\to  C]]></fr:tex> be <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000W/" title="Inverse" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000W/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000W/" type="local">invertible</fr:link> maps. Then the composite <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g\circ  f\colon  A\to  C]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000W/" title="Inverse" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000W/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000W/" type="local">invertible</fr:link>.</html:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" title="Jon Sterling" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>2</fr:month><fr:day>11</fr:day></fr:date><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>By <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002C/" title="From quasi-inverses to coherent inverses" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002C/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002C/" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002C/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002C/" /></fr:link>, it suffices to find a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000X/" title="Quasi-inverse" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000X/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000X/" type="local">quasi-inverse</fr:link> to the composite <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g\circ  f]]></fr:tex>; we take this to be the composite (<fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002L/" title="Composition of quasi-invertible maps" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002L/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002L/" type="local">Construction <fr:contextual-number uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002L/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002L/" /></fr:link>) of the underlying <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000X/" title="Quasi-inverse" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000X/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000X/" type="local">quasi-inverses</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
